name: Granny Fran's Feline Frenzy
description:
All of the stray cats in the neighborhood know that Granny Fran will be there to take care of them and find them new homes. 

But when they all decide to start coming in on the same day, things start going wrong!

Help Granny Fran get as many cats to new loving owners as possible... before the long arm of the law reaches out to shut her down!

Built by the Brown family for Ludum Dare 42. Z and L did the art and sound!
